caseTitle: Workers Party Pakistan thr. Akhtar Hussain v. Federation of Pakistan & others
authorJudge: MR. JUSTICE TASSADUQ HUSSAIN JILLANI, HCJ
tagline: The Court, in an application filed with a grievance that the directions given by this Court in the judgment reported as Workers Party Pakistan v. Federation of Pakistan (PLD 2012 SC 681) have not been complied with, seeks parawise comments from the Secretary, Election Commission of Pakistan and report from Election Tribunals Lahore and Multan.
